"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Polygon在周一的博客文章中宣称，Polygon Zero的“Plonky2”技术在速度和可扩展性方面树立新的里程碑，这可能是以太坊吞吐量方面的一个重大突破。 Polygon团队在博客中写道，“Plonky2是一种递归SNARK，是现有替代方案速度的100倍，并且与以太坊完全兼容。它结合了PLONK和FRI的优点，具有快速证明和不需要信任的设置；还结合SNARKs的优点，支持以太坊上的递归和低验证成本。” 据此前报道，Polygon以4亿美元收购零知识技术开发商Mir，将其更名为Polygon Zero。\",\"timestamp\":1641886871,\"title\":\"Polygon公布Plonky2，称其为世界上最快的ZK扩容技术\"},\"digest\":\"wN29yyR6RPMUakhEb9aTdqaKYwS51-WPF_ok5DHY7_s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xFacBD07B7808E7D3aa0938c67d591f01e25dD23F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"yah3Zi3wPwb2mAvHigrF-EbOfgfYneNugnFEkvgoFiU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Saryq5pHaP-07C05Dd1Zzm1hwzrZa3JakgR5ikQoPVk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"7kVP1msP2uz3lE_5ltEQLMPbAlOHiBSF2t3R1oGa9l7qhKvWFzaA4O_7qitP1biuy08aL-BHypv9Y1zc4zTXGQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x710a3451a80b804f053bd6031827bc4460637fa2f6453bf7e1122046a52f51c003fb92bcd222b69d93293c30ba1a54d3392806dd687fe41fb7e50d016f80787b1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"yah3Zi3wPwb2mAvHigrF-EbOfgfYneNugnFEkvgoFiU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Saryq5pHaP-07C05Dd1Zzm1hwzrZa3JakgR5ikQoPVk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"wN29yyR6RPMUakhEb9aTdqaKYwS51-WPF_ok5DHY7_s\"}"